TI  - The impact of non-pharmaceutical interventions on the spread of COVID-19 in Saudi Arabia: Simulation approach
AU  - Ahmad Alhomaid
AU  - Abdullah H. Alzeer
AU  - Fahad Alsaawi
AU  - Abdulaziz Aljandal
AU  - Rami Al-Jafar
AU  - Marwan Albalawi
AU  - Dana Alotaibi
